title: Re: ‘LOVE it when you have these liberal journalists stuttering’: Tucker Carlson takes on USA TODAY editor
text:
‘LOVE it when you have these liberal journalists stuttering’: Tucker Carlson takes on USA TODAY editor Posted at 10:20 pm   William A. 
Tucker Carlson had USA TODAY deputy editorial page editor David Mastio on Wednesday night to discuss a recent editorial that drew comparisons between Steve Bannon and ISIS leader Abu Bakr al-Baghdadi. 
Here is the video: 
Over the top? . @TuckerCarlson : “I get that you don’t like Steve Bannon…but comparing him to the head of ISIS, over the top. No?” #Tucker pic.twitter.com/ei7JuRVsFX 
— Fox News (@FoxNews) February 9, 2017 . @DavidMastio : When Steve Bannon gives ISIS a strategic victory it is a really big deal -TCT #Tucker 
— Tucker Carlson (@TuckerCarlson) February 9, 2017
